{
  "stem": "3475.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next day, they called out my name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they sent me out to another Kommando, which was also a technical Kommando.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's what saved my life.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I spoke up, because I had the courage to walk up to him.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because everybody was terrified of him, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He used to give people a [GERMAN], you know, and, and knock him down, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess it worked [LAUGHS] for me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So then I was sent to another Kommando, which was a lot better.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We used to transport acetylene bottles and the oxygen bottles, which they use in welding.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so that was a lot easier.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I worked closer with some German technicians-- craftsmen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Do you remember any of their names?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I remember there was one man who used to bring me a sandwich almost every day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was one of the craftsmen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I guess he had a heart.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he used to bring me a sandwich every-- he used to share his lunch with me every day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that-- I guess that was a bright, bright side of it, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And, and that lasted until the Germans started-- I mean, the Russians-- the Russians started getting closer.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we could-- we could hear the artillery booming.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, the planes were dropping bombs all around at Buna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we were hoping it would drop on the Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Unfortunately, I think they missed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But they did damage the factories, you know, and the installations.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say, probably 1994, 1994.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1944.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm sorry, [LAUGHS] I said '94-- wishful thinking.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, it was 1944, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Germans were coming in closer and closer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they evacuated Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
